\subsection{Costs}

\subsubsection{A courtesan must pay 250 + [350 \x Rank] Silver Pennies
per year for finery and the props of the trade.}

A courtesan who does not spend the above amount operates as if she were
two Ranks less proficient.  If the Rank of a courtesan is reduced to
a negative number, the use of the skill is temporarily lost.  The
above amount does not include extraordinary aids, such as love
philtres, but does include perfumes and other frippery.
